<paragraph base="F16130701" id="IFRS12_23" principles="no"><paranum>23</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 12"/><data name="paranum" value="23"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS12_P0164" outputclass="keep_with_next">An entity shall disclose:</p><ol base="F16130703" id="IFRS12_L0035" type="lower-alpha"><li id="IFRS12_23_a"><li_value>(a)</li_value>         <p base="F16130704" id="IFRS12_P0165">commitments that it has relating to its <xref base="F16124099" href="../ias28/IAS28_3.dita#IAS28_3/IAS28_P0021">joint ventures<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0211"/></ph></xref> separately from the amount of other commitments as specified in <xref base="F16228658" href="IFRS12_gB18-B20.dita#IFRS12_gB18-B20" id="IFRS12_X0175">paragraphs B18&#x2013;B20</xref>.                    </p>       </li><li id="IFRS12_23_b"><li_value>(b)</li_value>         <p base="F16130706" id="IFRS12_P0166">in accordance with <xref base="F16228661" href="../ias37/IAS37_TOC.dita#IAS37_TOC0001" id="IFRS12_X0177">IAS 37 <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Provisions, Contingent Liabilities and Contingent Assets</ph></ph></xref>, unless the probability of loss is remote, contingent liabilities incurred relating to its interests in joint ventures or <xref base="F16124075" href="../ias28/IAS28_3.dita#IAS28_3/IAS28_P0016">associates<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0018"/></ph></xref> (including its share of contingent liabilities incurred jointly with other investors with <xref base="F16124097" href="../ias28/IAS28_3.dita#IAS28_3/IAS28_P0020">joint control<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0208"/></ph></xref> of, or <xref base="F16124103" href="../ias28/IAS28_3.dita#IAS28_3/IAS28_P0023">significant influence<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0355"/></ph></xref> over, the joint ventures or associates), separately from the amount of other contingent liabilities.</p>                </li></ol></body></paragraph>